legacy.full_text: As Du Mu, a renowned Tang Dynasty (618-907) poet once said, "Across ten miles in #Yangzhou, the #spring breeze blows where; Behind the bead curtains, no one to my love could compare", Yangzhou is beautiful year-round but truly shines in the #spring. Watch the video to explore!😍 https://t.co/gZYiP7i4iE
